---
import { Navigation } from '~/components/navigation';

import '~/styles/globals.css';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />

    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Courgette&family=Inter:wght@400;700;800&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />

    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="favicon-32x32.png" />

    <meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />

    <title>Frontend Mentor | News homepage</title>
  </head>

  <body>
    <Navigation client:load />

    <main class="content flex flex-col gap-16">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-y-16 gap-x-8">
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-y-6 gap-x-8">
          <picture class="col-span-full">
            <source srcset="/image-web-3-desktop.jpg" media="(min-width: 1024px)" />
            <img src="/image-web-3-mobile.jpg" alt="Hero Image" />
          </picture>

          <h1 class="font-extrabold text-4xl lg:text-5xl">The Bright Future of Web 3.0?</h1>

          <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
            <p class="text-neutral-600">
              We dive into the next evolution of the web that claims to put the power of the
              platforms back into the hands of the people. But is it really fulfilling its promise?
            </p>
            <button
              class="bg-soft-red w-fit text-white px-6 py-2 uppercase tracking-widest transition-colors hover:bg-very-dark-blue"
              >Read more</button
            >
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-col bg-very-dark-blue p-4 lg:p-6 lg:py-8 gap-6 justify-between">
          <h2 class="text-soft-orange text-3xl font-bold">New</h2>

          <div>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-white text-xl hover:text-soft-orange transition-colors"
              href="#">Hydrogen VS Electric Cars</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-300">Will hydrogen-fueled cars ever catch up to EVs?</p>
          </div>

          <hr class="border-dark-grayish-blue" />

          <div>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-white text-xl hover:text-soft-orange transition-colors"
              href="#">The Downsides of AI Artistry</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-300">
              What are the possible adverse effects of on-demand AI image generation?
            </p>
          </div>

          <hr class="border-dark-grayish-blue" />

          <div>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-white text-xl hover:text-soft-orange transition-colors"
              href="#">Is VC Funding Drying Up?</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-300">
              Private funding by VC firms is down 50% YOY. We take a look at what that means.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="flex gap-4 h-fit">
          <img
            src="/image-retro-pcs.jpg"
            width="200"
            height="254"
            class="w-24 h-fit"
            alt="Reviving Retro PCs"
          />

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-neutral-300 text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">01</h3>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-very-dark-blue hover:text-soft-red transition-colors text-lg lg:text-xl"
              href="#">Reviving Retro PCs</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm lg:text-base">
              What happens when old PCs are given modern upgrades?
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img
            src="/image-top-laptops.jpg"
            width="200"
            height="254"
            class="w-24 h-fit"
            alt="Top 10 Laptops of 2022"
          />

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-neutral-300 text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">02</h3>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-very-dark-blue hover:text-soft-red transition-colors text-lg lg:text-xl"
              href="#">Top 10 Laptops of 2022</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm lg:text-base">
              Our best picks for various needs and budgets.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <img
            src="/image-gaming-growth.jpg"
            width="200"
            height="254"
            class="w-24 h-fit"
            alt="The Growth of Gaming"
          />

          <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
            <h3 class="text-neutral-300 text-2xl lg:text-4xl font-bold">03</h3>
            <a
              class="font-bold text-very-dark-blue hover:text-soft-red transition-colors text-lg lg:text-xl"
              href="#">The Growth of Gaming</a
            >
            <p class="text-neutral-600 text-sm lg:text-base">
              How the pandemic has sparked fresh opportunities.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <footer class="pt-16 pb-6 text-center">
      Challenge by <a
        href="https://www.frontendmentor.io?ref=challenge"
        target="_blank"
        class="text-soft-red hover:underline">Frontend Mentor</a
      >. Coded by <a href="https://znagy.hu" target="_blank" class="text-soft-red hover:underline"
        >Zétény Nagy</a
      >.
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
